name: InkCartridges
overview:
Ink Cartridges (www.inkcartridges.uk.com) are a cartridge retailer based in Leeds (UK).

They provide low cost cartridges, both genuine and compatible products, UK wide. They have years of expertise within the industry and will do their best at helping you get everything you need to start printing.

All their prices include VAT and free delivery, so the price you see is the price you get. Furthermore they guarantee all their compatible products so you can be sure that you are getting excellent quality.
